Sem 7

Sem 7

Banking & NI Act

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTtI_lmJSsyvYvGhNoO0CUmv6t6-1JcqC

History of money, law, and more about money. If you've wondered why pieces of paper with a dead guy's image or rectangular numbered plastics are important, you can find the answers here.

Environmental Law

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTtI_lmJSsyvhG6b2s8tNumHaLQtNKqTN

Environment is important, but alas, due to the tragedy of commons, no one really cares about it. We still needed some international and local cooperation, so we came up with environmental law.

IPR

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTtI_lmJSsyuN79GLo5q7BpuPeiG_o7D7

Intellectual Property rights refers to the rights you have over your intellectual property. It can be a pretty cool concept, if you think about it, though conventional copyright/patent is kinda pointless. To the best of my ability, this page is licensed under WTFPL. Because knowledge is free.

Corporate Law

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTtI_lmJSsyvJ1h8FwYDvjaN3QnKTCnaM

Some stuff starting with Companies Act. Honestly, I'm not as familiar with this one as the above ones, so just drop me a message if you prefer to write this description (or edit any above one).
